author: Daniel Greene
description:
Welcome back to another episode of Bookshelf Roasting! 📚🔥
In this video, I dive into the photos you've submitted and provide my honest (and possibly brutal) opinions on your bookshelf setups. Whether you're a minimalist, a maximalist, or somewhere in between, no shelf is safe from roasting.

Want your shelf featured in the next roast? Join the discord server: https://discord.gg/95mbwUQB
